[Intro: Soyeon & Becky G]
[?]
[?]
Yeah, yeah

[Verse 1: Thutmose]
Moving too fast like I&#039,m moving in slow-mo
I&#039,m a God better ask if you don&#039,t know
Homie better put your pride aside

Ay, no one can stop us they&#039,ll try but they won&#039,t
Ay, nada nos puede parar, oh, no!

Spinning this thing, gold on my ring, royalty up in my veins

빨리 달려 넌! 못.따.라. 와~
True Damage we do it, True Damage 보여줄게 뭐든 쉽게
이기든지든, my crew make the beat drop

[Pre-Chorus: Becky G]
Ay, no one can stop us they&#039,ll try but they won&#039,t (They won&#039,t)
Ay, nada nos puede parar, oh, no!

[Chorus: Keke Palmer]
We&#039,re wide awake now, our eyes are wide open
We&#039,re running this world, we keeping it turning
We&#039,re living like giants, yeah, giants
We&#039,re bigger than giants, we&#039,re giants
Oh, oh, oh, oh

Oh, oh, oh, oh

Mm, I keep on shattering time
I might just leave you behind
Homie, you stuck on rewind (Yeah, yeah, yuh)

When I damage your delicate spine
Please don&#039,t act all shy and surprised
They be like (Huh?), they be like
What you mean (Uh), what is your winning scheme? (Woo)
I got a giant team (Guess what?), big as my self esteem
Run it back, run it back, running man (Run it)
They think they go hard I&#039,m like come again (Sheesh)
You run out of time when I&#039,m bustin&#039, in, while you stumbling
I got this blade in my hand for your punishment

[Chorus: Keke Palmer, Becky G, & Thutmose ]
Oh, we&#039,re wide awake now, our eyes are wide open
We&#039,re running this world, we keeping it turning
We&#039,re living like giants, yeah, giants
We&#039,re bigger than giants, yeah, giants
Ya thought that we were weak, but we coming right back

[Post-Chorus: Soyeon, All]
Sleeping giants, sleeping, sleeping giants
